Properties.EnglishScriptText: [[How fascinating.]] Time itself? I never would have imagined such a thing.
[[How awful.]] I'm not sure what that means – but it sounds – horrible.
[[Did you attend Hogwarts?]] I wondered – did you attend Hogwarts?
